sources.name: pq_import_superstore
sources.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> pq_import_superstore

typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared pq_import_superstore = let
  AdfDoc = Sql.Database("rubicon-dev.database.windows.net", "canyonlands", [CreateNavigationProperties = false]),
  InputTable = AdfDoc{[Schema = "raw", Item = "superstore"]}[Data]
in
  InputTable;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = pq_import_superstore,
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(Source, {{"Order Date", type date}, {"Sales", Currency.Type}})
in
  #"Changed column type";
